name: Skinny dipping on Mermaid's planet.
description: Hi there! I heard about one mermaid, two planets away from us, that dreamed of a skinny dip on every planet in the Universe. One day, she decided to dye her hair pink and followed her dream. When she skinny-dipped around every corner of the Universe, she chose her favorite planet and moved there. Now, she skinny dips in the pink sea, with pink whales below the water and white swans swimming around her.
